{"tid":1759940,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"幾時清算差佬好","createTime":"2019-11-28T01:56:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-29T19:19:34.000Z","uid":61672,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"4e58032afdf4f8dd8baa71398fa96d9fa95e7358","tid":1759940,"uid":61672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T01:56:43.000Z","msg":"抗爭完左<br />\n區議會選完<br />\n<br />\n差佬仲有支助去換車牌<br />\n殺人強姦犯仲可以北上叫雞食海底撈？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【文宣核彈】搞左呢份野等三萬黑警都要接受國際審判<br />\n<br />\n[重Post] 話說我地花左兩個月時間, 睇左過百條片, 終於<br />\n我地製作左文宣核彈, 係 270 頁黑警濫權獨立調查報告<br />\n<br />\n但係咁岩撞正連登熄登,<br />\n無咩人推, 幾日過千正評都無<br />\n我好灰, 但我唔會放棄<br />\n唯有硬著頭皮, 開新 Post 推多次<br />\n同法律港女一樣, 我地會做實事,<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">依家搞緊英文翻譯, 然後就會製作文宣, 推向國際, 推向全世界<br />\n到時係聯合國好, 海牙好, 紐倫堡好, 美國國會, 英國國會, 歐盟<br />\n全部都係我地射程範圍<br />\n但係真係要大家廣傳, 所以希望大家真係唔好俾呢個POST 沉<br />\n好多人睇到唔訓覺, 工都辭埋, 甚至要抑鬱睇精神科<br />\n大家都係想香港贏, 香港人贏, 所以唔該唔好等我地心血白費<br />\n<br />\n中文版本&mdash;公眾試閱版&mdash;正文<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1N1rzVWFW0EnJugLGNkYu7A-9-KigPWn4fVEGVDve79k/edit\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fdocument%2Fd%2F1N1rzVWFW0EnJugLGNkYu7A-9-KigPWn4fVEGVDve79k%2Fedit&d=iBLSwy1tqwhlDNpwtuM9DQxAEvDk8dns9g3QPAGj3dU%3D&h=53b0d4ad\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/document/d/1N1rzVWFW0EnJugLGNkYu7A-9-KigPWn4fVEGVDve79k/edit</a><br />\n警隊涉嫌濫權資料（六／七月）<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1RMY12ApIxNTaOudzjvYXzq6Vc0iE99zJJ2M8t0uOKYI/edit\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fdocument%2Fd%2F1RMY12ApIxNTaOudzjvYXzq6Vc0iE99zJJ2M8t0uOKYI%2Fedit&d=iBLSwy1tqwhlDNpwtuM9DQxAEvDk8dns9g3QPAGj3dU%3D&h=0cf17b5f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/document/d/1RMY12ApIxNTaOudzjvYXzq6Vc0iE99zJJ2M8t0uOKYI/edit</a><br />\n警隊涉嫌濫權資料（至八月十日）<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1TKPNvv_YqRKF8Y2wRi28J89-VTMIsfNAiFsuXX4g1r8/edit\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fdocument%2Fd%2F1TKPNvv_YqRKF8Y2wRi28J89-VTMIsfNAiFsuXX4g1r8%2Fedit&d=iBLSwy1tqwhlDNpwtuM9DQxAEvDk8dns9g3QPAGj3dU%3D&h=1aeda26e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/document/d/1TKPNvv_YqRKF8Y2wRi28J89-VTMIsfNAiFsuXX4g1r8/edit</a><br />\n同埋！！！極重要<br />\n英文版好快就會係連登／ＴＷＩＴＴＥＲ／ＦＢ流出！！！<br />\n<br />\nSOURCE:LIHKG<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n[size=6]<span style=\"color: red;\">呢班人一定要受國際審判</span></span>"},{"pid":"cd27995334b378c6ed3bd4a298f7c308d3688931","tid":1759940,"uid":61672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T01:57:03.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"288051c713bcde5bb72ad94203be866eec5e0675","tid":1759940,"uid":61672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T01:57:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d4e3247493793b086385202b4936ab492a3474c","tid":1759940,"uid":61672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T01:57:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eae070d27faf3dfd704f5d2a20355f5ca9fc707a","tid":1759940,"uid":61672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T01:57:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b7dcb6073a47cd4a561dd662ca4f2c6d9e1c8e6","tid":1759940,"uid":61672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T01:57:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"deeb41e4aa8bbe206d782a78a80932e9542fcce6","tid":1759940,"uid":61672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T01:57:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56fce69fdb65b23a6251148b511e71c555b32ae9","tid":1759940,"uid":61672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T01:58:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kil